description:
A somewhat large thrusting sword that Knight Reisha can also use for slashing.
The blade, shimmering gently like the wind-blown surface of a lake, signifies
respect for the opponent. It is the result of meticulous care.
name: Windrider's Estoc
note: 初期ダンジョンで装備

description:
Worn-out mining tools. If used as a weapon, they are reduced to mere metal
bludgeons.
name: Dirty Pickaxe

description:
Strictly speaking, it's not equipment, but the spirit of 'rampaging to one's
content' is a weapon in itself. What was handed over from the store was an
embarrassing outfit and a full meal. Let's repay this kindness with our fists.
name: Sturdy Fist

description:
The blade that changes color reflecting its surroundings has the property of
absorbing the magical power around it. The fact that this beautiful sword is now
in her hands is proof that her journey and encounters were not in vain.
name: Frontier Land, Waterfall Sound Sword
note: アカネと共闘時に装備

description:
A shining sword that repaired its broken blade with the power of the royal
blood. If it's lost, then search for it; if it's broken, then mend it; if it's
heavy, then support it together.
name: Treasured Sword: Dawn Sword

description:
A broadsword too crude for a knight to use. Emphasis is placed on killing power
due to its weight and on sustained combat capability due to its sturdiness.
Also, due to its commonality, if one discards it on the battlefield, it's
unlikely to be traced back to the owner.
name: Broadsword

description:
An axe-spear dropped by an elite soldier from the magical research institute. It
has small magic ore crystals embedded in it. Although a powerful weapon, it is
very heavy and gradually saps the life force of its wielder. [Skill addition
available]
name: Elite Soldier's Halberd

description:
A sword with a broken blade. Bathed in sunlight, it sparkles and seems as if it
has completed its duty and rests in peace.
name: Broken Sword

description:
A man-made magic sword created from the royal blood after extensive magical
research. The blade is always wet with red and creates moons upon the earth. It
ultimately led to madness, but it was also the crystallization of a man who
believed in the power of human knowledge until the end.
name: Artificial Magic Sword: Red Moon Sword

description:
A typical iron sword, but with a special crystal attached to the guard that can
enhance the physical abilities of its user.
name: Iron Sword

description:
Metallic blunt weapon. "What's needed isn't technique but strength. It's
straightforward, and I like that."
name: Mace

description:
A blunt weapon with a weight attached to a chain at the end of a stick, held
with both hands. Since the tip moves freely, if you block the stick with a
sword, the momentum increases and the weight flies towards you.
name: Flail

description:
A light but well-made dagger. It can be used for various purposes. In combat, it
is more effective in fighting against humans than against monsters.
name: Thief's Knife

description:
A decorative royal scepter held by a monarch, hardly ever used in battle. For
some reason, it contains multiple layers of designs related to magical power
inside, but few people know about this now.
name: Royal Scepter
